Reasoning: The paper discusses the problem of diagrammatic reasoning and proposes a solution using a Knowledge-based Long Short Term Memory (KLSTM) framework. This involves analyzing and understanding visual information, which is a core problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed framework also involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI), and the comparison with state-of-the-art learning frameworks suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE) in the proposed framework.
